Have you been in an accident? Are you being unlawfully treated by Sec? Are you in need of help with legal documents? Did Epi cause you bodily harm?
Then Exo-Law & Associates might be able to help you. Our skilled lawyers handle many cases with strict adherence to Space law!
Our local station representative is always ready for a non-binding conversation in case you advice or direct legal action.

